Name:           sesdev
Version:        1.12.1+1619444076.g04475be
Release:        1%{?dist}
Summary:        CLI tool to deploy and manage SES clusters
License:        MIT
URL:            https://github.com/SUSE/sesdev
Source0:        %{name}-%{version}.tar.gz
